OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fbegins cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,7,Fshowery rain. Drier conditions return
OL,8,Ffor a time from the late evening. Low
OL,9,Fcloud and further outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Fspread north towards morning, with the
OL,11,Fchance of some patchy fog.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FThe morning will be cloudy
OL,14,Fwith outbreaks of rain, this heavy at
OL,15,Ftimes, the odd fog patch. The rain
OL,16,Fwill clear to sunny spells and showers
OL,17,Flater in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
