OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,6,Fclearing early Saturday otherwise the
OL,7,Fweekend will be mostly dry and bright
OL,8,Fwith some sunshine. Monday mostly dry,
OL,9,Fbright, but chance of rain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
